      <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-580ada5edea241039e5ae1da27468866" font="1|Sans|9.0|1|GTK|1|" textAlignment="1">
        <bounds x="384" y="480" width="373" height="109"/>
        <content>Requirements Management for AARM-EG is implemented through:
1. GitHub eaclawai repo - Architecture Requirements Repository
2. FAB-UC-001.md - LLM-consumable requirements baseline
3. Pull Requests - Requirements Impact Assessments
4. Commit history - change traceability across ADM cycles</content>
      </child>
